---
source: crates/runtime/tests/metadata/mod.rs
expression: explain_met_size_filtered
---
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: met_size.id ASC NULLS LAST, met_size.size ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |   Filter: met_size.size = UInt64(2319)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |     TableScan: met_size projection=[id, value, year, month, day, size], partial_filters=[met_size.size = UInt64(2319)]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [id@0 ASC NULLS LAST, size@5 ASC NULLS LAST]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   SortExec: expr=[id@0 ASC NULLS LAST], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |     FilterExec: size@5 = 2319                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|               |       BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
|               |         DataSourceExec: file_groups={3 groups: [[hive_partitioned_data/year=2022/month=1/day=1/data_0.parquet, hive_partitioned_data/year=2022/month=1/day=2/data_4.parquet], [hive_partitioned_data/year=2022/month=3/day=3/data_2.parquet, hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=2/day=2/data_1.parquet], [hive_partitioned_data/year=2023/month=4/day=1/data_3.parquet]]}, projection=[id, value, year, month, day, size], file_type=parquet |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
+---------------+-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
